'''佳雅特麗·戴維'''（{{lang-en|Gayatri Devi}}，{{lang-hi|गायत्री देवी}}，{{bd|1919年|5月23日|2009年|7月29日|catIdx=D}}）<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/royalty-obituaries/5934077/Rajmata-Gayatri-Devi.html "Rajmata Gayatri Devi"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/royalty-obituaries/5934077/Rajmata-Gayatri-Devi.html |date=20220209121837 }}. The Telegraph. 29 July, 2009.</ref>是[[印度|印度]][[土邦|土邦]][[齋浦爾|齋浦爾]]（Jaipur state）最後一任[[拉者|摩訶拉者]]{{tsl|en|Man Singh II|萬·辛格·二世}}（Man Singh II）的第三位[[拉者|摩訶拉妮]]（1940年－1949年在位）。<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/people/Ive-had-a-happy-life-with-no-regrets-Gayatri-Devi/articleshow/4834617.cms "I’ve had a happy life, with no regrets: Gayatri Devi"] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/people/Ive-had-a-happy-life-with-no-regrets-Gayatri-Devi/articleshow/4834617.cms |date=20210211004118 }}. The Times of India. 29 July, 2009.</ref>1947年，萬·辛格·二世把土邦和剛獨立的印度合併並可保留所有頭銜。戴維的兒子{{tsl|en|Prince Jagat Singh|賈格·辛王子}}（Jagat Singh）在1970年繼位，佳雅特麗·戴維成為齋浦爾土邦王太后（Maharani Gayatri Devi, Rajmata of Jaipur），

戴維是[[庫齊比哈尔|庫齊比哈尔]]摩訶拉者Jitendra Narayan和[[巴罗达土邦|巴罗达土邦]]公主Indira Raje之女。[[印度獨立|印度獨立]]後，戴維成為一名政治家。她以美貌及時尚打扮著名。<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-34344537 "Grandchildren win India royal Gayatri Devi's riches"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-34344537 |date=20201225043538 }}. BBC UK. 24 September, 2015.</ref>

